  "title": "A bright blue UFO seen in Curitiba [2003]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/11/a-bright-blue-ufo-seen-in-curitiba-2003/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-iM",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>FEB 27th, 2003</strong>. Time; 5 pm. Duration: 40 seconds. In the city of Curitiba, State of Paraná, a witness in the neighborhood of Portão reported the sighting of an unidentified flying object in the shape of a bright blue star. The UFO was apparently stopped, but then was  seen flying towards the Northeast. The witness reported that the visibility conditions were good, without the presence of clouds, and that there was also no visible record of sound or trail emitted by the sighted object.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.632. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário com relato sobre avistamento de Ovni em Curitiba, Paraná&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>FEB 27th, 2003. Time; 5 pm. Duration: 40 seconds. In the city of Curitiba, State of Paraná, a witness in the neighborhood of Portão reported the sighting of an unidentified flying object in the shape of a bright blue star. The UFO was apparently stopped, but then was  seen flying towards the Northeast. The witness [&hellip;]</p>\n",
